sequenceDiagram
    actor Player
    participant System
    
    Note over Player, System: UC-09: Search Hidden Location
    Player->>System: clickStaticObject(object)
    Player->>System: selectAction("SEARCH")
    
    System->>System: deductEnergy(searchCost)
    System->>System: checkHiddenInventory()
    
    alt Item found
        System-->>Player: displayMessage("Found Item X")
        System->>System: transferItemToInventory(item)
        opt Item is Target Item
            System->>System: trigger "Game Won" sequence
        end
    else Nothing found
        System-->>Player: displayMessage("Nothing found")
    end